Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.69,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... But you at least managed \Nto play it to the en—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.07,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,About that, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:24.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized, I'm supposed \Nto do vocals too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:32.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't sing while I'm focusing \Nall my motor control on the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:38.51,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it might be better \Nfor the band if I just sang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.81,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But then I wouldn't have anything \Nto do during interludes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd probably start fidgeting on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.54,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd better work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.32,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:53.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Her eager self-improvement power \Nis too bright to look directly at!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.53,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure it's all right\Nfor me to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You should sing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.25,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.50,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Is it that unpleasant a thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.98,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.58,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some new guitar showmanship move?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:15.68,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:16.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:18.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll practice it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to practice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo's here, so let's meet up at the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the band meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's today's topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The question:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.95,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnArial Black\blur0.3\fs36\c&H080A05&\pos(354.702,75.309)}How can we be\N more band-like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,How can we be more band-like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.45,DefaultItalics,Hitori & Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's so half-assed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.48,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.85,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.23,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.98,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.62,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.99,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.63,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.46,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:30.42,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.84,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:40.64,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.77,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:50.83,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.82,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:03:00.83,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:05.58,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HB3750D&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HB5780F&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(416.5,255)}#04 Jumping Girl(s)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.96,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnArial Black\blur0.3\fs30\c&H080A05&\pos(353.564,70.759)}How can we be\N more band-like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've got a full member lineup,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured the first order of business \Nwas to get us acting more band-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.37,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:25.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I know practice is crucial,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but there's gotta be more to us than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should talk \Nabout all kinds of stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to give Kita-san \Na break from all her practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,One tactic is to nail the \Nsuperficial stuff first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.01,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that totally works!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Like if you start imitating a new popular \Nmake-up technique and end up looking great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.09,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they're speaking \Na foreign language...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And with that in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I made us band merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's a more superficial \Nstarting point than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just put a zip tie around your wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, huh? They come in all colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.64,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sell them for 500 yen a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What a ripoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.76,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,650 if they're signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What a steal! I'll take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that just be circulating \Nmoney within the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else with ideas \Nfor becoming more band-like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can set us up an Isstagram and run it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby appoint you \NMinister of Social Media!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll post every day when the time comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What about forming a fan club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's awfully hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.26,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 yen annual membership fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's awfully expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.54,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Membership perks include meet-and-greets
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.11,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and a once-a-year takoyaki party with the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.61,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The fans bring the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What a steal! I'll join!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, you're already in the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.19,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? I wasn't even thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Her eyes are so sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.81,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the burden of expectation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-If I don't say something, I... I...
