Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We settled on it before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo would write the music, \Nand you'd write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.50,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got off-limits words, \NBocchi-chan, you should write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.50,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.66,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.96,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I can't wait to hear \Nyour song, Ryo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Have you written it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.92,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.54,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it once I get inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And Minister of Lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, it's so cool that \Nyou took on such a tough job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I can write lyrics \Nlike nobody's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.57,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's the super-easiest thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You get carried away so easily, Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna write the most band-like lyrics \Nand guarantee us a huge hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,"Band-like"?
