Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.71,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.97,0:06:07.47,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my priorities in order?!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.47,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Jimihen's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.63,DefaultTop,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Futari!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I already spent five hours yesterday \Nediting video to escape reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid! I'm a paramecium!
