Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-san's gonna be singing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerful lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A seishun song, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.54,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I could easily write depressing lyrics, \Nof course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.59,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I've gotta write something band-like, \Nwith real Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.83,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in the mind \Nof cheery person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an extrovert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who surfs in the pool at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who claims the title Queen of Woot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Woot! Woot! Woot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Woot! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some vibes up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tequila shots in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not a cheery person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,it's just a party animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.52,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No more shortcuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You must {\i0}become{\i1} Kita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Come over now if you wanna go to Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone takes Isstaworthy pics right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.21,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be launching fireworks in ten mins, \Nso let's take pictures together then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.40,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I know an exorcist, if you need one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's n-n-n-not like that!
