Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, no seishun songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try a song of encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:48.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I personally find status-quo-affirming \Nlyrics annoyingly irresponsible, but...
