Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shallow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:17.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Any depressed person hearing this song \Nwould just drop deeper into despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.15,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't this an intervention \Nwhere you tear into me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:35.07,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)\c&H281616&\fs12\3c&HD2C2C0&\bord2\frz350.1\frx5\fax0.05\pos(319.5,212.5)}I failed to write the lyrics I was assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,for failing to write lyrics \Ndespite all the bragging I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's perverse! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you call us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think of it until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but there's one other really \Nband-like thing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Take ProPhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.23,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Promotional photos, she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:56.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Since Bocchi-chan isn't in \NKessoku Band's current ProPho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Current?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.29,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We took it for our last concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, since Kita-chan ditched us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:06.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such an awful ProPho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:13.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So, because it's nice out today \Nand none of us have plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured we'd take a few ProPhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the money \Nto rent a studio, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:25.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Taking public pictures in Shimo-Kita \Nis too much to ask of a nerd like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We could do it in Starry \Ninstead if you prefer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but a ProPho is important \Nfor conveying a band's direction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:34.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and the unique qualities of its members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So we really need to give it \Neverything we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We need something that'll have impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:44.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,whether it's in a club ad online, \Na flyer, or a magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.06,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.67,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I resign myself to this fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Resign yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I declare this ProPho-scouting journey on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.33,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's la go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:54.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.86,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,A fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,With plants...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,At the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:15.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I think we've covered all the bases \Nfor broke band ProPhos...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and an evocative wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.59,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,223)\fnArial Black\c&HEFF9FA&\3c&HB64F05&\frz279.4\fax-0.2\pos(558,96.5)\blur0.3}Milkus Water
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we'd brought our instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Having our instruments \Nmight make us look cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,For you guys, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Only guitarists and bassists \Nlook cool that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What about the poor drummer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck just holding up my drumsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.89,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But that's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's swap instruments, just for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.16,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:55.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,With all these posters up, it has \Na real "Shimo-Kitazawa" vibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.28,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be a CD shop I went to a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:10:59.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:05.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of record shops and club venues \Nclosing these days, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.93,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Shops that have been there for decades, \Ndisappearing one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo, you were just celebrating \Nthat new book store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.79,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I love B&C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, don't let Ryo jerk you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ninety percent of the things she says \Nare more or less just for vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.81,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But Senpai can jerk me around \Nany time she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:31.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.67,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:39.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought I saw a\Nn-nice-looking wall over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Taking it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:51.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're definitely capturing everyone's \Npersonalities, but it's not really band-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a way to really \Nmake it scream "band"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,As I am the quintessential musician,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.74,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,you need only mimic my expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to know where you \Nget all that confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't go wrong doing what Senpai says!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,A pair of yes-men, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.91,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're at a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.92,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:18.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But Kita-chan looks cute in any pic we take!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like you know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:28.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess it's because I upload pics \Nto Issta all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.18,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.33,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Minister of Social Media!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.65,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Gotoh-san? Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.39,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! She's flopping around like a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:44.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never taken pictures \Nwith friends before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:44.07,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? Please, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Since... I never {\i0}had{\i1} friends before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The only pictures I've taken \Nthat weren't with family
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,were class pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,With those as my only proof of existence \Nfor the past fifteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Bocchi-chan's weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:01.55,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there are any other \Nhigh school girls like me still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I've become a rare species, \Non par with the tsuchinoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.53,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I am... I am the tsuchinoko \Nof Shimo-Kitazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san's saying the strangest things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, this is normal for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.60,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Noko-noko. Noko-noko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, why don't you \Nstart your own Isstagram?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:18.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.14,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to be a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.07,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,we should really have \Nindividual member accounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to get an account...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with self-esteem so bad \Nshe's already trying to form a band
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,to get popular despite \Ntotal social ineptitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If s-someone like me were to \Nstart an account like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You would witness the birth of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The attention-whore monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.95,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Like my posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.64,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Like my posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My video site is all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.69,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:10.57,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We won't push you to get on social media anymore!\NPlease come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:17.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, back to the ProPhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's really hitting the spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.67,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about a jump pic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Jump pic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's really photogenic, and it could \Nbring out everyone's personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.27,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! You're a genius, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,A wise man once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.62,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,any anime where they jump in \Nthe OP is a god-tier anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:39.34,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Would jumping in our ProPho \Nthus make us a god-tier band?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she getting that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I followed your logic there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.00,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Five, four, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-can't even remember \Nthe last time I jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.99,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.58,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see Bocchi's undies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's one hell of a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for putting something \Nso worthless in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:14:59.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping for a cuter reaction there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even jump properly, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! It's got the band feel \Nand the seishun thing going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I could get \Na copy of that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:19.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're feeling band-like now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we're one step closer \Nto becoming a popular band!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.53,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kessoku Band is getting started for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have our concert in summer (TBD),
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,our demo CD sale (TBD),
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,our first album release in winter (TBD),
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:37.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and become Shimo-Kitazawa's own \Ngood vibes-iest vibes-band!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.14,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's a lot \Nstill to be decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even have a song yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:47.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I t-totally forgot about the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we've got Ryo and \NBocchi-chan on the case, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She must have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What a total free spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The more time that passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:06.02,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b0\c&H02151E&\frz27.02\fax0.15\blur0.3\pos(271,129.5)}Lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,the higher the lyrics bar seems to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-If I show them this and \Nthey're mean to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Or worse, if they're \Nobviously humoring me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:17.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe I should show it to \Nsomeone and see how they react.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.00,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Ryo-san would ever humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H1C1A18&\b0\frz9.93\fax0.1\pos(271.65,59.9)}Ryo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H1C1A18&\b0\frz9.93\fax0.1\3c&HBDBAB8&\bord3\pos(172.22,126.22)}a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H1C1A18&\b0\frz9.93\fax0.1\3c&H65BA6F&\bord3\pos(344,131)}It's a pleasure to make contact with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs15\c&H1C1A18&\b0\frz9.93\fax0.1\3c&H65BA6F&\bord3\pos(267.5,193.5)}This is Bocchi speaking\N\hIf you happen to still be in Shimo-Kita,\N\hdo you think you might be able to\N\h\hconsider having a look at my lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\b0\frz9.93\fax0.1\pos(246,222.5)\c&HBBB6B8&}Read
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She already read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&H1C1A18&\b0\frz9.93\fscx110\fax0.1\3c&HBDBAB8&\bord3\pos(273,268.5)}I'm here, come by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A t-trendy café!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.55,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\3c&HB59997&\c&H5E4D81&\bord2\pos(214.5,113)}Congratulations \N{\c&H48353A&}on Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.55,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\3c&HB59997&\c&H4A3C60&\bord2\pos(382.5,99.5)}Congrats on opening
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.55,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\3c&HB59997&\c&H5E4D81&\bord2\pos(449.5,81.5)}Congrats, {\c&H48353A&}La Chic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.55,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\3c&HB59997&\c&H5E4D81&\bord2\pos(514.5,34)}Congratulations, {\c&H48353A&}La Chic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to a real \Nrestaurant by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:41.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even enter a convenience store \Nwithout psyching myself up in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:48.82,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy100\t(23,7489,\fscy105.19)\fscx100\t(23,7489,\fscx105.19)\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\3c&HE0D0CB&\c&H5B4689&\bord2\fax-0.16\frz9.876\move(539,32.5,548.19,25,23,7489)}Congrats on opening
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I allowed to just walk in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.43,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How do people just walk into places?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How do they do it on TV and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Are ya winning, diners?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.72,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.95,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I've never \Nbeen alone with Ryo-san before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know much about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,F-For that matter, why hasn't \Nshe talked to me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.01,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She finished eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? Should I initiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.59,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That photo shoot sure was fun, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.44,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That could be the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.88,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Just show me the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:41.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.35,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.16,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.86,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's unusually flustered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I agree, \Nbut for the band's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:04.39,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(358,1)\fnComic Sans MS\b0\blur0.3\c&H0D0E0A&\fs19\pos(404,112)\frz17.5}Gotoh
