Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.63,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Though personally I think one\Nis a bit childish for a band.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the right page!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you personally satisfied \Nwith these lyrics, Bocchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, w-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I figured we should do something \Nreally "hit band"-like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.12,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\blur1\pos(20,20)\p1\c&HF5F8F5&\fscx300\fscy215\alpha&H33&}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.12,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs12\an7\c&H787C77&\pos(30,30)}Can't do it anymore\NYou say as you give up on moving forward\NOn a road that seems to go on forever\NIt feels like you'll never arrive anywhere\NAnd that's got you worried, doesn't it?\N\NBut hey now, listen up\NDon't forget you're not alone, that we're all here\NWe're sending you this cheer just as your heart's about to break\N\NYour dreams will come true\NDon't give up until the very end!\NYour dreams will come true\N{\s1}Believe in yourself the way you are{\s0}\NBelieve in yourself and get walking again!\N\NGlory awaits you ahead, I know it\NFor everyone around the world trying hard, Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Did I ever tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:26.12,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I was in another band a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:32.08,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Their lyrics were awkward, \Nbut I liked how honest they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.47,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But, desperate for sales, they started \Ngoing in a more commercial direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.34,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I hated that. That's why I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We had a little fight about it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.64,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And just as I was feeling sick \Nof the whole band thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:53.66,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.15,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got time, \Nwill you play bass for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.28,Flashback,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.45,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love the way you play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:06.29,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,When Nijika said that to me, I decided \Nto give playing in a band another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.42,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning your uniqueness \Nis equivalent to dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:17.42,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So don't write generic lyrics \Nbased on other concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.26,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Write what {\i1}you{\i0} want to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:25.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if I do that, I'll write bitter, \Nsocial-outcast lyrics—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But won't it be hilarious\Nif a normie sings that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.69,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I spend my days cursing you losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:37.40,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing a wide variety of individuals \Ntogether into one sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.28,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That's the color that Kessoku Band will have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san is actually a considerate person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.11,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ryo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The check...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.68,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm broke. Treat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.27,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you're the one who invited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.68,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't take another \Nday of eating weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.24,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You're still doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:09.52,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And this shop just opened, \Nand I wanted to eat here so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.31,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Please, treat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I t-take back what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.80,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry. \NI'll pay you back next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No need to rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I f-finished the lyrics...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, are you all right? You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.69,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been so focused on the lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-completely forgot to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see the \Nfruits of your labors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It m-might be... too much of a downer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.01,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is a downer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:12.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But it's very Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.26,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It might not connect with too many people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:21.34,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,but those it does, it'll hit deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd this friendship come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But these lyrics really are \Nsuper great, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I love this phrase here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.20,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I m-managed to figure out the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:58.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the band can \Nstay together forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:03.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and I can get lots of \Npictures with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:21.34,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep, with big problems \Nweighing down on me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:32.00,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you can’t beat that feeling \Nof being loved, it’s true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:41.68,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I awaken from cold dreams, \Nmy body feels numb
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:50.42,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shine so brightly, \Nit could make me a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:55.30,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s time to take that step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:03.02,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Though there’s nothing certain about it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:10.15,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It carries my childish heart into tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.52,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s time to blast out the thoughts \Nrattling around in my brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:17.10,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,And live, to its fullest, a life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.10,0:23:22.08,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been taking advances on for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.59,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also love the days I spend \Nlying around, doing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.21,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know I’m going to go see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:33.01,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it all disappears some day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:39.89,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H078AE5&\pos(309,49.5)}#05 Flightless Fish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:39.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it.
